{
  "stem": "10587.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wouldn't dare go to the infirmary, because that would be the end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So friends would help me along.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I somehow, you know, being young guy, I-- I recovered from that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but I didn't want to do anything to go to another transport, because I wasn't completely healed yet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember one-- one morning, we were out on the report platz, which is where they count, and everything took place on this platz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we were kept there for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was-- the rumor had it that Eichmann, you know, is coming to inspect the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] his troops, you know, his sacrificial lambs.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were there for quite a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Many people just couldn't stand any-- couldn't take it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They just keeled over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a lot of people died that day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I gradually felt better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- Did you see Eichmann that day?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I-- yes, I saw him that day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what happened?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did he walk around to everyone?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- we would never come close to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he would-- he didn't want you-- have you-- lice and all the diseases and all of the-- they were very-- you know, they were-- that's why they wouldn't touch you with their hand.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They always used the rifle butt or-- whatever they had, a stick or a whip.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a-- a whole entourage of SS troopers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and I-- I think that I-- I saw him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I can't-- among them, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the rumor had it that Eichmann is-- you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you were not allowed to talk in the ranks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they were whispering anyways, because they wouldn't get-- get near you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were only counting in front or looking at the side and behind you, but never were inside the ranks.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And if they wanted to send someone in, they would usually send in the kapo to get you out or whatever punishment you should receive.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was starting to feel better, and I-- and there was a transport going to the Krupps factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I-- also was not my barracks, but-- so I went to-- got undressed, I went and got into the line, and-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I saw Mengele.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe he was standing a little bit behind you, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It means turn around, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says-- he didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he sent me where all these old people went and the ones that couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I realized that I'm-- I'm doomed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but I never put my clothes back on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I somehow maneuvered to get back with the people that were standing in the nude.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the other people, they said, you can get dressed, the ones that-- there were two selections made always-- the ones that were sent on a transport and the ones sent to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At least this is the experience that I-- and that's how I realized what was happening when I saw the sick and the lame and the old.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] as I came closer-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to-- you had to stay in the line.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the lines get pretty long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, they take a few hundred people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so-- and they walked-- they called Mengele for something-- I don't know-- for a phone call or some-- in other words, he told his assistant, was a-- like Mengele must have been like maybe a Hauptsturmfuhrer, and the other guy must have been a Sturmfuhrer.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he called him, and he said to take over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I go-- and they said to me-- in the line, says-- when I got in the line, the guy's standing there and say, remember, when he asks you [SPEAKING GERMAN], tell him, [SPEAKING GERMAN]-- metalworks.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because the rumor had it that this transport is going to the Krupps factory, to Funfteichen.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At that time, we didn't know-- we didn't know the name of Funfteichen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But that's what really happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I got back, and this young man, this Sturmfuhrer says, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so I turned around, and he said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he sent me to the right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how I got out of Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to Funfteichen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I want to ask you a couple things about Auschwitz, OK?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Since that's what we're talking about, before you get to the Krupps factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First, I know that you said that you knew that people died in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
